Tasmanian Devil Analysis

Peptide Tables

The .raw files were analysed for four experiments in Peaks 8.5 with 1% FDR and 80% ALC for de novo identifications.

The .raw files were analysed for three experiments in MaxQuant with 1% FDR, match between runs, and using the label free quantification module.

Both sets of analysis used the database incorporating variant sequences identified from the transcriptome analysis.

Assays A-C represent the tripilcate assays from 2017, Assay D represents the assay from 2016.
